snippet.title: Arthur: The Tibble Super Action Challenge
snippet.description:
Tommy and Timmy Tibble are tested by their own knowledge to figure out each question as trivia to the Arthur show. In the words of D.W. Read, there are four rounds of five questions. Tommy and Timmy will have a few seconds to choose an answer for each question. If time runs out, before they answer, they will not get any points. 

Subscribe to my channel!
